---
title: Tandoori Cauliflower & Spinach Rice Pilaf with Mint Yoghurt & Pickled Cucumber
description: Pilaf has to be one of our favourite ways to enjoy basmati rice, and roasting is our number-one way to cook cauliflower, so this dish is destined for greatness! We've added tandoori flavours, plus mint yoghurt and crunchy pistachios to seal the deal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e72e81a87eb2f1ddf497ab0-344b86c0.jpg
